scattered localities in mainland NE 
<collectingCountry box="[3145,3308,1958,1997]" name="Vietnam" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
(Na H.a. Nature Reserve and Ba Be and Cue Phuong national parks).
